---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="聯絡我 - 個人網站" description="與我聯絡，討論技術或合作機會">
  <Navbar />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 gradient-bg">
    <!-- Starry background -->
    <div class="starry-space">
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
      <div class="star"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
        >
          聯絡我
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          無論你是對我的作品有興趣、想一起合作，還是單純聊聊開發、遊戲、AI
          應用，都歡迎透過以下方式聯絡我。
          我樂於結識志同道合的夥伴，一起創造更多可能！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 聯絡內容 -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- 聯絡表單 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            傳送訊息
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            如有任何問題或合作想法，歡迎隨時聯絡我，我會盡快回覆，期待與您交流！
          </p>

          <form
            name="contact"
            method="POST"
            data-netlify="true"
            netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
            class="space-y-6"
          >
            <!-- Honeypot 防護欄位 (隱藏) -->
            <div style="display: none;">
              <label
                >Don't fill this out if you're human: <input
                  name="bot-field"
                /></label
              >
            </div>

            <!-- 隱藏的form-name欄位 -->
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />

            <!-- 姓名 -->
            <div>
              <label
                for="name"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                姓名
                <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="name"
                name="name"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white transition-colors"
                placeholder="請輸入您的姓名"
              />
            </div>

            <!-- Email -->
            <div>
              <label
                for="email"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                Email
                <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white transition-colors"
                placeholder="your@email.com"
              />
            </div>

            <!-- 主旨 -->
            <div>
              <label
                for="subject"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                主旨
                <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="subject"
                name="subject"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white transition-colors"
                placeholder="想要討論的主題"
              />
            </div>

            <!-- 訊息內容 -->
            <div>
              <label
                for="message"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                訊息內容
                <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
              </label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                rows="6"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white transition-colors resize-none"
                placeholder="請詳細描述您想要討論或合作的內容..."></textarea>
            </div>

            <!-- 提交按鈕 -->
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="w-full px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              傳送訊息
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>

        <!-- 聯絡資訊 -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- 聯絡方式 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              其他聯絡方式
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Email -->
              <div
                class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3
                    class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                  >
                    Email
                  </h3>
                  <a
                    href="mailto:dianyike1013@gmail.com"
                    class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline"
                  >
                    dianyike1013@gmail.com
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- GitHub -->
              <div
                class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg"
              >
                <div
                  class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.237 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3
                    class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                  >
                    GitHub
                  </h3>
                  <a
                    href="https://github.com/dianyike"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline"
                  >
                    github.com/dianyike
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 預留社群連結位置 -->
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600"
                >
                  <div
                    class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded-full mb-2"
                  >
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >待新增</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600"
                >
                  <div
                    class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded-full mb-2"
                  >
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >待新增</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600"
                >
                  <div
                    class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600 rounded-full mb-2"
                  >
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >待新增</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 常見問題 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              常見問題
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- FAQ 1 -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3
                  class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                >
                  Q:為什麼沒有FaceBook、Instagram等社群連結？
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                  A:目前我的 Facebook 和 Instagram
                  帳號暫時無法使用，正在積極協助恢復中，恢復後會盡快補上相關連結，感謝您的理解與耐心等待。
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- FAQ 2 -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3
                  class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                >
                  Q:為什麼帳號無法使用？
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                  A:近期帳號遇到安全問題，正在加強保護並申請恢復中。未來會更加留意帳號安全，避免類似情況再次發生。感謝您的關心！
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- FAQ 3 -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3
                  class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                >
                  Q:為什麼沒有提供電話聯絡方式？
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                  A:為了避免接收到不必要的廣告或騷擾電話，目前僅提供電子郵件與社群媒體作為主要聯絡方式。如果您有正式合作或面試需求，歡迎來信聯絡，我會視情況提供電話號碼，並安排進一步的聯絡。感謝您的理解與配合！
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 回應時間說明 -->
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-primary-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-primary-900/20 rounded-lg p-6"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3
                  class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                >
                  回應時間
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                  平日 10:30 至 00:00
                  聯絡我，通常可於一小時內收到回覆；其他時段的來信將於下一個工作日回覆。若遇假日，回覆時間可能會稍有延遲，敬請見諒。
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
